snippet.title: StarFox EX Launch Trailer Official
snippet.description:
Download the Mod from Romhacking.net here: https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/7285/
For more information, join the discord! http://discord.gg/sfex

After 2 years in development, the greatest StarFox mod is finally FINISHED! Thank all of you for the continuing support, the team hopes you guys enjoy it, have fun!

Star Fox EX: Exploration Showcase Features a TON of modifications and improvements to the original game including:

A new Full map with over 15 new levels!
2-5 players mode that works with a real Multi-tap!
3+ page Pre-Game Config/Mod Menu!
Customizable Ships, Weapons and Crosshairs!
Full Camera Control and Alternate Views!
30-60 FPS Super FX Mode!
New Bosses!
30+ New Music Tracks!
Super Scope, NNT Pad & Mouse Support!
Scored Mode!
Endurance Mode!
Dark Mode!
Tons of hidden secrets!

And many more additions!

Enjoy, and Good luck!

-kandowontu
Twitter: https://twitter.com/kandowontu

Trailer by Kert Gartner
Twitter: https://twitter.com/kertgartner
